#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.64"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.64:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:0.2"
msgid "7. Arahantavagga "
msgstr "7. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.64:0.3"
msgid "64. Maññamānasutta "
msgstr "64. When You Identify "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.75, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.64:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn22.64:1.3"
msgid "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu … pe … ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

# NOTE: Maññati in such contexts means “think about in terms of a self”. Nyanamoli/Bodhi try to capture this with “conceive”, punning on “conceptualize/conceit”. But the pun is highly obscure without a detailed knowledge of the issues. Using “identify” I am trying to make the subtext clearer.
#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:1.4"
msgid "“Maññamāno kho, bhikkhu, baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "“When you identify, mendicant, you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:1.5"
msgid "amaññamāno mutto pāpimato”ti. "
msgstr "Not identifying, you’re free from the Wicked One.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:1.6"
msgid "“Aññātaṃ, bhagavā, aññātaṃ, sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "“Understood, Blessed One! Understood, Holy One!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.64:2.1"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how do you see the detailed meaning of my brief statement?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:2.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, bhante, maññamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "“Sir, when you identify with form you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:2.3"
msgid "amaññamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not identifying, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:2.4"
msgid "Vedanaṃ … "
msgstr "When you identify with feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.64:2.5"
msgid "saññaṃ … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.64:2.6"
msgid "saṅkhāre … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.64:2.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ maññamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "consciousness, you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:2.8"
msgid "amaññamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not identifying, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:2.9"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief statement.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.64:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu. "
msgstr "“Good, good, mendicant! "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.2"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi. "
msgstr "It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in brief like this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:3.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, bhikkhu, maññamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "When you identify with form you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.4"
msgid "amaññamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not identifying, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.5"
msgid "Vedanaṃ … "
msgstr "When you identify with feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.6"
msgid "saññaṃ … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.7"
msgid "saṅkhāre … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ maññamāno baddho mārassa; "
msgstr "consciousness, you’re bound by Māra. "

msgctxt "sn22.64:3.9"
msgid "amaññamāno mutto pāpimato. "
msgstr "Not identifying, you’re free from the Wicked One. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:3.10"
msgid "Imassa kho, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti … pe … "
msgstr "This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what I said in brief.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.64:3.11"
msgid "aññataro ca pana so bhikkhu arahataṃ ahosīti. "
msgstr "And that mendicant became one of the perfected. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.64:3.12"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

